title: Opel Vauxhall CD70 Navi Central Europe maps 2008
description:
The latest maps for Central Europe (2008) for Opel CD70 Vauxhall GPS NAV system.

Tested and working.

My way:
1. Mount with Daemon Tools
2. Burn with Nero: CD Copy -> enable "on the fly" -> source drive: virtual mechanic -> speed 32x


Detailed coverage for:

SLOVENIA
SLOVAKIA
CZECH REPUBLIC
HUNGARY
CROATIA
POLAND
ESTONIA
LATVIA
LITHUANIA
GREECE

Other European countries main roads only and street address for their capitals.

Enjoy!
